<doc id="1091952" wikidata="Q31152" url="?curid=1091952" title="Hilde Hildebrand">
<text>Emma Minna Hilde Hildebrand (10 September 1897 – 12 May 1976) was a German actress born in Hanover, Germany on 10 September 1897. She died at the age of 78 in Grunewald, Berlin, on 27 May 1976.
 
