* A Tutorial of the RDMA Model
* &quot;Why Compromise?&quot; // HPCwire, Gilad Shainer (Mellanox Technologies), 2006
* A Critique of RDMA for high-performance computing
* RDMA Reads: To Use or Not to Use?</text><links>
